**Fenrir** | Werewolf Killing | Haunted
__Basics__
Every other night, the Fenrir may banish one ghost. The Fenrir may still do so while a ghost themself.
__Details__
If they choose not to banish, they will once again have the option to banish in the following night.
Banishing a ghost is an end-night ability.
The Fenrir is a member of the wolfpack and a lycan.

__Simplified__
Every other night, the Fenrir may banish one ghost. The Fenrir may still do so while a ghost themself.

__Formalized__
Haunted Role
Inherit: `Pack Lycan`
End Night: Banish @Selection[ghost] [Succession: No Succession]

__Card__
Fenrir is beyond the mortal world: they may banish ghosts.
